\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces DDInter validation results (test set n=11,150, optimized thresholds). \textbf  {(A)} Dumbbell chart comparing exact accuracy (filled circles) vs.\ adjacent accuracy (hollow circles) across methods; calibrated methods achieve 66.4\% exact and 99.3\% adjacent accuracy with Cohen's $\kappa $=+0.096. \textbf  {(B)} Radar plot showing multi-metric comparison: calibrated methods (green) outperform baseline (red) across all dimensions. \textbf  {(C)} Raincloud plot showing keyword score distributions by DDInter ground truth severity; half-violins display density, boxplots show IQR and median, jittered points show individual samples. Substantial distribution overlap explains the classification ceiling. \textbf  {(D)} Score discrimination summary: Major (+0.93 $\pm $ 1.33, n=2,464), Moderate (+0.07 $\pm $ 1.48, n=8,193), Minor ($-$0.28 $\pm $ 1.25, n=493); error bars = $\pm $1 SD. All metrics from \texttt  {validate\_against\_ddinter.py}.}}{6}{}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:validation}{{2}{6}}
